data.eml:eml: Description of Paraceto gen. n. and a relimitation of the genus Cetonana (Araneae: Trachelidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Zhang, Feng (2017): Description of Paraceto gen. n. and a relimitation of the genus Cetonana (Araneae: Trachelidae). Zootaxa 4320 (2): 225-244, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4320.2.2
